title: Gold Strong Padded Bubble Envelopes Lightweight Peel & Seal Cushioned Protective Packaging for Posting, Shipping & Mailing (100, STG 1 (110 x 165))
features: PADDED BUBBLE ENVELOPES: Our Gold kraft bubble padded envelopes offer exceptional protection for your valuable items during transit with their high-quality bubble padding, shielding them from impact and damage. These Bubble Envelopes feature a peel-and-seal closure. The inside is lined with bubbles, making the product secure and safe. Padded envelopes are Waterproof and lightweight.

SAVE ON POSTAGE COSTS: Our envelopes are lightweight and we only use the best materials to make our kraft bubble mailers. You can ship your packages with confidence using our strong and long-lasting padded bubble mailers. Bubble envelopes are a low-cost and effective way to ship all of your packages. These great for the home and office and ideal for businesses and e-commerce orders.

SMOOTH SURFACE: Easy Identification: Each envelope features a smooth surface that allows for easy labelling and writing, ensuring clear identification of the contents and reducing the chances of misplacement. The sleek gold exterior of our padded envelopes adds a touch of elegance and professionalism to your mailed items, making a positive impression on recipients. We also have a massive range of sizes to choose from.

SIZE DIMENSIONS: Internal measurements in MM: STG 1 (110 x 165), STG 2 (120 x 215), STG 3 (150 x 215), STG 4 (180 x 265), STG 5 (220 x 265), STG 6 (230 x 340), STG 7 (240 x 335), STG 8 (270 x 360), STG 9 (300 x 445), STG 10 (350 x 470), CD (165 x 170) & DVD (170 x 215mm) Approx.
